{
  "id": "6388141ef117e9001ea1a65c",
  "title": "KJ法は枚数が2倍になると4倍難しくなる",
  "created": 1669862571,
  "updated": 1669863292,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6388141ef117e9001ea1a65c",
      "text": "KJ法は枚数が2倍になると4倍難しくなる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669862571,
      "updated": 1669862571
    },
    {
      "id": "6388164eaff09e00005969c7",
      "text": "10枚のラベルから2枚選ぶ組み合わせは",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669862991,
      "updated": 1669863206
    },
    {
      "id": "638814abaff09e00008b101c",
      "text": "[$ 10 \\times 9 \\div 2 = 45]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669862571,
      "updated": 1669862951
    },
    {
      "id": "63881661aff09e00005969c8",
      "text": "20枚のラベルから2枚選ぶ組み合わせは",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669863010,
      "updated": 1669863209
    },
    {
      "id": "638814adaff09e00008b101d",
      "text": "[$ 20 \\times 19 \\div 2 = 190]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669862573,
      "updated": 1669862975
    },
    {
      "id": "6388162aaff09e00001b3791",
      "text": "で、4.2倍に増えている。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669862954,
      "updated": 1669863029
    },
    {
      "id": "6388166eaff09e00005969c9",
      "text": "この「枚数が2倍になると2枚の組み合わせ方を検討するのにかかる時間は4倍になる」が枚数の多いKJ法の難しさのベースになっている。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669863023,
      "updated": 1669863138
    },
    {
      "id": "638816e1aff09e00005969cb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669863138,
      "updated": 1669863138
    },
    {
      "id": "63881717aff09e00005969cd",
      "text": "ラベルを1枚ずつめくることに比べると、広いスペースに広げて視線を動かすだけで見渡せるようにすることは「次のものを見る」コストを下げる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669863191,
      "updated": 1669863276
    },
    {
      "id": "63881746aff09e00005969ce",
      "text": "しかし人間の目の解像度の限界で、一度に見渡すことができる枚数に限界がある。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669863239,
      "updated": 1669863274
    },
    {
      "id": "6388176faff09e00005969cf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669863279,
      "updated": 1669863279
    },
    {
      "id": "6388176faff09e00005969d0",
      "text": "関連",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669863279,
      "updated": 1669863283
    },
    {
      "id": "63881772aff09e00005969d1",
      "text": "　[並べて一覧性を高くする]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669863283,
      "updated": 1669863292
    },
    {
      "id": "63881692aff09e00005969ca",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669863058,
      "updated": 1669863058
    }
  ]
}